OL,3,CMan due in court in Lancashire charged
OL,4,Cwith online threats to Commons Speaker
OL,6,FLancashire Police have charged a man
OL,7,Fwith making online threats to the
OL,8,FChorley Labour MP and Commons Speaker
OL,9,FSir Lindsay Hoyle.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Force said, "A
OL,12,Fman was arrested following a report of
OL,13,Fan offensive and threatening message
OL,14,Fsent via social media.
OL,16,F"Following enquiries a man in his
OL,17,Ffifties from Chorley has been charged
OL,18,Fwith two counts of malicious
OL,19,Fcommunications and has been bailed to
OL,20,Fappear at Preston Magistrates Court on
OL,21,FMay 23."
