OL,3,CMan due in court in Lancashire charged
OL,4,Cwith online threats to Commons Speaker
OL,6,FSir Lindsay himself revealed he had
OL,7,Freceived online abuse in an interview
OL,8,Ffollowing the announcement that the
OL,9,FConservative Justice Minister Mike
OL,10,FFreer is standing down at the next
OL,11,Felection. The London MP said repeated
OL,12,Fthreats and an arson attack on his
OL,13,Fconstituency office had left him too
OL,14,Ffearful to carry on his work.
OL,16,FMr Freer and his staff had been
OL,17,Finformed that Ali Harbi Ali had
OL,18,Fwatched their Finchley office before
OL,19,Fgoing on to murder fellow Conservative
OL,20,FMP Sir David Ames at his office in
OL,21,FSouthend in 2021.
