OL,3,CMan due in court in Lancashire charged
OL,4,Cwith online threats to Commons Speaker
OL,6,FSir Lindsay Hoyle said: "Of course
OL,7,FMike has been through a lot. I
OL,8,Funderstand him saying 'Enough is
OL,9,Fenough', and I respect that"
OL,11,FHe said he had been threatened in
OL,12,Fposts online on Friday 26 January: "I
OL,13,Ffaced threats as well and the police
OL,14,Fhad to make an arrest on the basis of
OL,15,Fthreats that are coming in all the
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,18,F"I got lots of that and it shouldn't
OL,19,Fgo with the job but unfortunately it
OL,20,Fdoes come with the job."
